snippet: Ms. Taylor co-founded the Dorian Wind Quintet in 1961, and remained with it for 40 years as it became one of the premier ensembles to feature flute, oboe, clarinet, French horn and bassoon.
abstract: Jane Taylor, bassoonist and co-founder of the Dorian Wind Quintet, dies at age 79.
lead_paragraph: Ms. Taylor co-founded the Dorian Wind Quintet in 1961, and remained with it for 40 years as it became one of the premier ensembles to feature flute, oboe, clarinet, French horn and bassoon.
